{"tid":232300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗警民衝突一男一女被捕　警員被指使用過度武力","createTime":"2017-05-06T16:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T06:53:14.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75a1dc703a7d284d879b182b40ab3a40b4f2d4b8","tid":232300,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"元朗警民衝突一男一女被捕　警員被指使用過度武力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-06-2017/37683?utm_content=bufferd6a76&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-06-2017%2F37683%3Futm_content%3Dbufferd6a76%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter.com%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9cef5421\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-06-2017/37683?utm_content=bufferd6a76&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"7b5c129b93806086ff647877aa6768e8c0c58a96","tid":232300,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:03:33.000Z","msg":"有網民今日（5月6日）上載一條短片到「North District 北區」Facebook 群組，片段記錄了一宗警民衝突，有一男一女先後被捕，網民批評警員在拘捕過程中使用了過度武力。 片段所見，一名手無寸鐵的白髮男子，被多名警員制伏，而該男子就不斷高呼「差人打人呀」。之後一名女子上前，與警員發生碰撞之後，有警員隨即指她襲警，並從後箍了該女子的頸，將她制伏。 <br />\n<br />\n據《東網》報道，當時有水務處人員到元朗八鄉打石湖村進行水務工程，但遭到一名男居民阻止，隨後水務員人員報警。 警方發言人回應指，昨日（5月5日）早上接獲一名公職人員報案，指在元朗粉錦公路一屋苑執行職務時遇到阻礙，要求警方協助。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場調查後，以涉嫌妨礙公職人員執行職務及拒捕，拘捕了一名61歲姓張男子，警方亦以涉嫌襲擊警務人員罪名，拘捕一名59歲姓陳女子，案件交由元朗警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-06-2017/37683?utm_content=bufferd6a76&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-06-2017%2F37683%3Futm_content%3Dbufferd6a76%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter.com%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9cef5421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-06-2017/37683?utm_content=bufferd6a76&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"5d6d55e9de316ad7e79c13dc06e3705d9a7f3ce9","tid":232300,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c88c54959576a828e3557c574f38a8b2f55badb","tid":232300,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"黑警係咁叫人冷靜。自己再唔冷靜<br />\n<br />\nOn99<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d4d8f048bd8afe506d51e7296e7dc7166f3ea6","tid":232300,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"一般老野都支持警察行使武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28393a2daeac299b56b81147961e19f7ecaa3b3","tid":232300,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"擺明想收陀地啦<br />\n打柒佢就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲牛屎佬都唔慌好人"},{"pid":"ff3dcf616eee6c252b97ce1ea9a8394564a4b81a","tid":232300,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"南亞打唔贏 咪搵市民發洩囉"},{"pid":"9262d234d7badf7cc6bbd36f001ef21cfbd0d4e6","tid":232300,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺明想收陀地啦<br />\n打柒佢就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲牛屎佬都唔慌好人</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真"},{"pid":"f55efd13e20a5f864848a5c3486eb98fb59486